column2: SELECT dbo.fCosmoDc(#,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT)# as distmin,   dbo.fCosmoDc(#,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT)+# as distmax,   p.ra AS pra, p.dec AS pdec, p.modelmag_r,   pz.z as photoz FROM Galaxy AS G   OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS n   LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid=p.objid   LEFT JOIN Photoz as pz ON n.objid=pz.objid WHERE    G.objID = n.objID    and dbo.fCosmoZfromDc(distmin,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT)<pothoz   and pothoz<dbo.fCosmoZfromDc(distmax,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT) INTO MyDB.NearbyObjEq5
